  <header>
    <h1 class="glow">PHYSDepot ⚛️</h1>
    <h4 class="glow">A repository of physics resources</h4>
  </header>

  <main>
    <p>Welcome!</p>
    <p><strong>PHYSDepot</strong> is a repository of physics resources helpful to physicists at all stages — from
      beginners to professional researchers. Our goal is to curate tools, packages, simulations, and educational
      materials that lower the barrier to entry and empower both students and scientists alike.</p>

    <p>Whether you are just beginning your journey or working on advanced research, PHYSDepot is built to support your
      work. This platform was inspired by the struggle many scientists face when access to mentorship and educational
      opportunities is limited. We aim to connect, unify, and enable exploration through science and learning.</p>

    <section id="contributors">
      <h2>Contributors</h2>
      <p>We always welcome new collaborators! To join, email <a href="mailto:abinau@iu.edu">Amelia</a> and
        <a href="mailto:rdube@iu.edu">Ricky</a>. To suggest resources, fill out our form (coming soon).</p>

